      "title": "Sajith's sister is suddenly called to CID; What is the reason?",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Opposition leader Sajith Premadasa's sister Dulanjali Premadasa has been summoned to the Criminal Investigation Department today in connection with the burning of President Ranil Wickremesinghe's residence.",
        "He said that he was near the then Prime Minister's house when the incident took place and that the crime investigation department told him to give a statement to help the investigations and he did so. (R)"
      ],
